{"tid":2509356,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［開電視］奇妙電視獲准用頻譜傳送免費電視服務　將新增一條頻道","createTime":"2021-04-29T11:14:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T11:42:33.000Z","uid":350584,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c7f35307107d5df5e7ce35494a1f6ceb83fadc41","tid":2509356,"uid":350584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:14:15.000Z","msg":"通訊局原則上批准奇妙電視的申請，除了使用固定網絡外，亦可使用頻譜作為免費電視服務的新增傳送模式。奇妙電視亦承諾除現有的兩條綜合頻道外，將提供一條新的數碼電視節目頻道。<br />\n<br />\n通訊局認為，原則上批准奇妙電視使用頻譜，符合觀眾的利益，為觀眾提供更多節目選擇。<br />\n<br />\n奇妙電視表示歡迎，將增設多一條頻道，製作更多優質節目，目標明年第一季開始試用頻譜廣播，明年底前推出新頻道。　<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1588437-20210429.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1588437-20210429.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=4YJm346n2OvV5E02CjQHwXNo2vAooDXMO4YLrfRUzdI%3D&h=8c21c01b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1588437-20210429.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=cbb44580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1588437-20210429.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"1627f7b075ea26db7f29e017a466f1b4aa6df87d","tid":2509356,"uid":350584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:15:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4od1pGm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4od1pGm.jpg&h=0ba3ed8b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"953338d4239c1c29e93ad4c8dc293dcadce19c7a","tid":2509356,"uid":350584,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:15:43.000Z","msg":"通訊局今日（29日）公布，原則上批准奇妙電視的申請，可使用一段新頻譜作為其免費電視服務的新增傳送模式，料於2021年12月1日完成遷移。奇妙電台亦承諾，會利用頻譜開設一個新的數碼電視節目頻道，即其免費台會由兩個變成三個。<br />\n奇妙電視表示，最快明年底可以「開新台」。"},{"pid":"925619252ac2522be2a60ec51ae34abfda6a2aef","tid":2509356,"uid":350584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:16:19.000Z","msg":"奇妙電視：明年底開新台<br />\n<br />\n奇妙電視發言人表示，將安排現有77台香港開電視及76台英文頻道香港國際財經台，採用頻譜傳送，並將增設多一條頻道，「製作更多優質節目，冀透過大氣電波服務更多觀眾。」但未有透露新台會主打哪類型節目及目標觀眾群。<br />\n<br />\n奇妙電視指，預計今年內完成具體的基建設置，在明年第一季開始試用頻譜廣播，目標是明年底之前推出第三頻道。<br />\n<br />\n除了利用頻譜廣播，奇妙電視會繼續使用固定網絡，將三個頻道的節目 傳送到用戶。"},{"pid":"080143f7773c192e725279452664cd17290d3016","tid":2509356,"uid":204309,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:17:27.000Z","msg":"做藝員有福<br />\n四周工作機會 搶人"},{"pid":"0e0068aa4c6adb85f2518217a5e829756c23e090","tid":2509356,"uid":64874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:17:38.000Z","msg":"1097有線雞騰聽日有得升番上一毫<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/vampire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baad6e67b0aa2507f7e5acbef7292caeb7715dd0","tid":2509356,"uid":350584,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:18:47.000Z","msg":"解決左大家話收唔到睇唔到既問題，依家冇藉口了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a46631c0f8a9a38c6a8e45d84048f96fb110139f","tid":2509356,"uid":350584,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:19:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Csd8O9s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCsd8O9s.jpg&h=19593741&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"472b632440c0952ae7078273757f7500df535603","tid":2509356,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1627f7b075ea26db7f29e017a466f1b4aa6df87d","tid":2509356,"uid":350584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:15:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4od1pGm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4od1pGm.jpg&h=0ba3ed8b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:20:38.000Z","msg":"個景係公廁定邊度黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ac37147a264e1ba2b1ef1d4ecf3c056cab5ebe5","